Package: libmeteo-vm2-tools
Section: misc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Library to work with VM2 weather samples (tools)
 Tools to handle VM2 files:
 .
 * bufr-to-meteo-vm2: BUFR to VM2 converter
 * meteo-vm2-to-bufr: VM2 to BUFR converter
 .
 This package contains a set of VM2 tools.

